					$('#ask-box').fadeToggle(150);
				}

			})

	function createTwitterLink(element) {
		var article = element.closest('article');
		var url = encodeURIComponent(article.data('permalink'));

		if(desc.length == 0) desc = encodeURIComponent($(article).find('section').text());
		
		window.open("https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Marshalls%20Project%20Fab:%20" + desc + "&amp;url=" + url +"&amp;hashtags=Marshalls", "_blank");
				
	}
	
	function createPinterestLink(element) {
		
		var article = element.closest('article');
		var images = $(article).find('header a');
		if(images.length == 0)
		{
			// if it's a photo permalink page this should populate
			images = $(article).find('header img');
		} 
		
		var media = "";
		var url = encodeURIComponent(article.data('permalink'));
		if(images.length &gt; 1) {
			// photoset. check to see which image is visible
			if($(images[0]).css('display') == 'none') {
				// first image is hidden. choose second image
				media = $(images[1]).find('img').data('500px');
			} else {
				media = $(images[0]).find('img').data('500px');
			}
		} else if(images.length == 1) {
			// photo post. pin the only photo
			// if images is an array of img tags, look in there. otherwise look for the img tags.
			var img = $(images[0]).is('img') ? $(images[0]) :  $(images[0]).find('img')[0];
			
			if($(img).data('500px')) {
				media = $(img).data('500px');
			} else {
				media = $(img).attr('src');
			}

				
		} else {
			
			// choose a generic
		}
		
		var desc = $(article).find('section h2').text();

		if(desc.length == 0) desc = $(article).find('section').text();
		
		window.open("http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=" + url + "&amp;media=" + media + "&amp;description=Marshalls%20Project%20Fab: " + desc, "_blank");

	}
	
	function openContentPage(element) {
		
		if ($(window).width() &lt; 768) {
		   // go to permalink
			window.location.href = element.data('permalink');		
		}
		else {

			// load in modal
			// clear out modal
			$('#permalinkModal .modal-body').html('');
			
			var content = element.closest('article');

			var cloned = content.clone(true).appendTo('#permalinkModal .modal-body');
			
			//update images with their larger counterparts
			$.each($('#permalinkModal img'), function(key, value){
				if($(this).data('highres'))
				{
					$(this).attr('src', $(this).data('highres'));
					
				} else if($(this).data('500px')) {
					$(this).attr('src', $(this).data('500px'));
				} 
			})
			
		   	// remove extra element styles sitting on thumbnail
			
			cloned.initArticleEvents();
			
			$('#permalinkModal .modal-body').attr('style', '');
			$('#permalinkModal .modal-body').removeClass('isotope');
			$('#permalinkModal .modal-body article').attr('style', '');
			$('#permalinkModal .modal-body div.photosetRow').attr('style', '');
			
			$('#permalinkModal').modal('show');
			
			
		}
	}
   </script>
